      <title>Indeed 称，伦敦就业岗位低于新冠疫情前的水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/london-jobs-are-settling-below-pre-covid-levels-indeed-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于混合工作模式减少了对办公室附近店员和咖啡师的需求，伦敦的职位空置率预计将保持在新冠疫情之前的水平以下，落后于英国其他地区。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/london-jobs-are-settling-below-pre-covid-levels-indeed-says</guid>
